<view class="imports-page">
  <view class="panel">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view><text class="eyebrow">导入</text><text class="title">导入地图或地点文件</text></view>
      <text class="tag">GeoJSON / KML / CSV / Photo</text>
    </view>
    <button class="primary-action" bindtap="chooseFiles">选择文件</button>
    <text class="help">CSV 只需要三列：名称、纬度、经度。一次最多导入 1000 个可显示点。照片导入只读取本地文件名和 EXIF GPS，不上传照片。</text>
    <view wx:if="{{files.length}}" class="file-list">
      <view wx:for="{{files}}" wx:key="id" class="file-row">
        <view class="file-copy"><text class="file-name">{{item.name}}</text><text class="file-meta">{{item.points}} 个地点 · {{item.lines}} 条路径/形状</text></view>
        <button class="text-danger" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="deleteFile">删除</button>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="panel">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view><text class="eyebrow">存档</text><text class="title">数据存档</text></view>
      <text class="tag">JSON</text>
    </view>
    <view class="archive-actions">
      <button bindtap="exportArchive">导出存档</button>
      <button class="danger-action" bindtap="clearAllData">清空全部数据</button>
      <button bindtap="chooseArchive">导入存档</button>
    </view>
    <text class="help">点亮地点、导入对象和打卡勾选都会保存到存档文件。恢复存档会覆盖当前小程序里的旅行数据。</text>
  </view>
  <view class="panel">
    <view class="section-head"><view><text class="eyebrow">数据检查</text><text class="title">数据检查</text></view></view>
    <view class="inventory">
      <view><text class="value">{{checkinCount}}</text><text class="label">地图打卡</text></view>
      <view><text class="value">{{pointCount}}</text><text class="label">导入地点</text></view>
      <view><text class="value">{{lineCount}}</text><text class="label">路径/形状</text></view>
      <view><text class="value">{{fileCount}}</text><text class="label">导入文件</text></view>
    </view>
    <view wx:if="{{!checkinCount && !pointCount && !lineCount}}" class="empty">暂无可检查的数据</view>
  </view>
</view>
